<title>USA: Playboy, Image strike DVD pact.</title>
<headline>Playboy, Image strike DVD pact.</headline>
<dateline>LOS ANGELES 1997-03-19</dateline>
<text>
<p>Image Entertainment Inc said it signed a deal with Playboy Enterprises Inc's home video unit under which it will license and distribute Playboy videos in the new digital video disk (DVD) format.</p>
<p>DVDs can hold one full-length, digitally produced movie in several differnt formats on a disk the size and shape of an audio CD, and electronics manufacturers hope DVD players will become the next generation of video players.</p>
<p>Image said it will release about 30 Playboy home video titles per year in DVD, beginning with the 1997 Playmate of the Year in May.</p>
